224
00:13:09,710 --> 00:13:11,980
Then let's watch that movie tomorrow.

225
00:13:12,380 --> 00:13:14,070
- It sounds fun.
- Yes.

226
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:16,110
- I'm looking forward to it.
- Me too.

227
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:20,730
I never imagined watching "Roman Holiday".

228
00:13:33,230 --> 00:13:35,620
