00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:02,520
How is the universe's goddess doing?

525
00:34:04,190 --> 00:34:05,790
She's fine.

526
00:34:06,260 --> 00:34:08,270
- You should get to work too.
- Right.

527
00:34:15,670 --> 00:34:18,490
Yes, Mr. Yeon. I saw the news too.

528
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:20,210
Lee Gang Joon is back in Korea.

529
00:34:21,410 --> 00:34:23,750
Nothing's out of the ordinary yet.

530
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:26,840
I doubt Yun Seo knows since
she never watches the news.

531
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,720
Yun Seo's on her way out.

532
00:34:29,720 --> 00:34:31,550
I'll call you later. Sure.

533
00:34:38,030 --> 00:34:40,650
All right. What is it?

534
00:34:41,030 --> 00:34:43,010
Whose call did you abruptly end?

535
00:34:43,930 --> 00:34:46,350
What? I did nothing of the sort.

536
00:34:47,640 --> 00:34:48,720
There.

537
00:34:50,170 --> 00:34:51,500
- Yun Seo.
- Yes?

538
00:34:54,140 --> 00:34:55,260
What is it?

539
00:34:55,710 --> 00:34:56,970
How are things these days?

540
00:34:57,410 --> 00:34:59,620
Has anyone been lurking around you...

541
00:35:00,050 --> 00:35:01,610
or following you around?

542
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:06,360
Hold on. Why are you asking me that?

543
00:35:07,660 --> 00:35:09,220
Isn't it obvious?

544
00:35:09,290 --> 00:35:10,560
You're Oh Yun Seo!

545
00:35:10,560 --> 00:35:14,330
You're so beautiful that
I'm constantly worried.

546
00:35:16,370 --> 00:35:18,060
Do I look good today as well?

547
00:35:18,130 --> 00:35:19,420
Yes, like always.

548
00:35:21,400 --> 00:35:22,690
- I'll get going then.
- Sure.

549
00:35:26,580 --> 00:35:27,630
Bye, Hyuk Joon.

550
00:35:27,680 --> 00:35:29,510
- Have a good day.
- You too.

551
00:35:41,260 --> 00:35:43,710
Yes, Mr. Kwon. Good morning.

552
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:46,670
The ruling? Hold on a second.

553
00:35:48,600 --> 00:35:49,620
Let me see.

554
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:53,440
Sure. Where should I send it?

555
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:58,740
I'm in the parking lot, so I'll
send it once I get up there.

556
00:35:58,740 --> 00:35:59,760
Don't worry.

557
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:01,000
I'll see you soon.

558
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:21,620
How are things these days?

559
00:36:22,030 --> 00:36:24,140
Has anyone been lurking around you...

560
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:26,100
or following you around?

561
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:35,260
How are things these days?

562
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:37,870
Has anyone been lurking around you...

563
00:36:38,270 --> 00:36:39,800
or following you around?

564
00:36:44,670 --> 00:36:45,730
Excuse me.

565
00:36:48,210 --> 00:36:49,850
Who are you...

566
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:51,550
and why are you following me?

567
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:56,570
- Well, your pen...
- You're a fan?

568
00:36:57,720 --> 00:37:00,320
You're mistaken, sir. I'm not a celebrity.

569
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:02,880
I'm just a normal girl who's
exceptionally pretty.

570
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:11,560
Hold on a second.

571
00:37:13,070 --> 00:37:14,770
Why do you keep following me?

572
00:37:14,770 --> 00:37:17,070
I already told you that
I'm not a celebrity!

573
00:37:17,070 --> 00:37:18,750
Wait. That's not it!

574
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:25,980
Unbelievable.

575
00:37:29,690 --> 00:37:32,890
Hi, honey. Yes, I'm at Jung Rok's law firm.

576
00:37:33,890 --> 00:37:34,910
Jung Rok?

577
00:37:36,090 --> 00:37:37,560
He's not answering his phone.

578
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:41,180
I'm almost at the office,
so I'll tell him face to face.

579
00:37:41,900 --> 00:37:43,030
Sure.

580
00:37:47,240 --> 00:37:48,770
How can I help you?

581
00:37:49,070 --> 00:37:51,590
I'm here to see Attorney Kwon Jung Rok.

582
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:53,650
Tell him that Kwon Jae Bok is here.

583
00:37:53,940 --> 00:37:56,710
You must be Mr. Kwon's father.

584
00:37:56,710 --> 00:37:59,440
How did you know that instantly?

585
00:37:59,520 --> 00:38:01,010
I just got a vibe.

586
00:38:01,980 --> 00:38:05,390
Anyway, his office is right down the hall.

587
00:38:05,390 --> 00:38:07,740
- Let me show you...
- No, it's all right.

588
00:38:08,390 --> 00:38:09,990
I can find my own way.

589
00:38:11,190 --> 00:38:15,210
The ruling is now sent.

590
00:38:21,370 --> 00:38:23,250
I can't believe you followed me in here!

591
00:38:23,510 --> 00:38:24,900
I'm not Oh Yun Seo...

592
00:38:30,810 --> 00:38:33,280
All right, fine. I am Oh Yun Seo.

593
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,780
Are you happy now?

594
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,990
- What?
- You said you were a fan.

595
00:38:37,990 --> 00:38:41,050
Are you happy now that
you caused me trouble?

596
00:38:41,790 --> 00:38:44,380
How did you know that I work here?

597
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:48,560
Just how much about me do you know?

598
00:38:58,740 --> 00:39:01,980
Look here, miss. I think there's
been a misunderstanding.

599
00:39:01,980 --> 00:39:03,550
I'm not a fan of yours.

600
00:39:03,950 --> 00:39:07,250
I just wanted to return
the pen that you dropped.

601
00:39:07,250 --> 00:39:08,920
- Sorry?
- Also,

602
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:12,220
I didn't follow you here.
I'm here to see my son.

603
00:39:13,490 --> 00:39:16,350
What do you mean you're
here to see your son?

604
00:39:16,790 --> 00:39:19,410
Isn't this Kwon Jung Rok's office?

605
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:22,840
- It is.
- See?

606
00:39:23,470 --> 00:39:27,200
I'm here to see Jung Rok, my son.

607
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:30,270
So Mr. Kwon is your...

608
00:39:34,580 --> 00:39:35,630
Sir!

609
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:39,680
Hello, sir!

610
00:39:46,790 --> 00:39:47,810
Father?

611
00:40:01,300 --> 00:40:03,150
Unbelievable.

612
00:40:04,240 --> 00:40:06,860
How could I treat his father that way?

613
00:40:21,390 --> 00:40:22,480
What brings you by?

614
00:40:25,390 --> 00:40:27,650
Why not wear something warmer?

615
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:30,140
Your neck's all exposed.

616
00:40:30,170 --> 00:40:31,430
You'll catch a cold at that rate.

617
00:40:33,640 --> 00:40:37,080
I'm making sure that I
stay healthy just fine.

618
00:40:38,340 --> 00:40:40,420
Call your mom often as well.

619
00:40:40,910 --> 00:40:42,810
That's something I've been working on.

620
00:40:42,810 --> 00:40:43,980
Seriously?

621
00:40:44,050 --> 00:40:46,230
Can't you just say "yes" for once?

622
00:40:46,420 --> 00:40:47,850
You always need to have the final say.

623
00:40:54,090 --> 00:40:56,680
The more I think of it,
the more annoyed I am.

624
00:40:56,860 --> 00:41:00,610
How can she think that I
followed her up here?

625
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:04,290
I'm worried to see that you have such...

626
00:41:04,330 --> 00:41:05,730
an irresponsible secretary.

627
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:09,890
All people make mistakes.

628
00:41:15,680 --> 00:41:19,080
Was this done by that secretary of yours?

629
00:41:21,580 --> 00:41:23,820
Is this a coloring book?

630
00:41:23,820 --> 00:41:25,830
Instead of coloring the boxes,

631
00:41:26,220 --> 00:41:28,310
she should spend that time doing more work.

632
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:31,190
She does what needs to be done around here.

633
00:41:31,190 --> 00:41:33,510
Her attitude says otherwise.

634
00:41:34,900 --> 00:41:37,630
Someone serious about their
work wouldn't dress like that.

635
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:41,370
You're being biased if that's
what you're judging her on.

636
00:41:41,370 --> 00:41:43,920
- Still, I can already tell how...
- Dad.

637
00:41:45,540 --> 00:41:47,550
Tell me why you're here.

638
00:41:47,640 --> 00:41:50,850
Does there have to be a reason for
a dad to come to see his son?

639
00:41:51,380 --> 00:41:52,840
This is my workplace.

640
00:41:53,750 --> 00:41:56,230
You came all the way here to
see me during working hours,

641
00:41:56,390 --> 00:41:58,540
so I thought it was because
of something urgent.

642
00:41:58,550 --> 00:41:59,650
Fine then.

643
00:42:00,360 --> 00:42:02,950
I'm sorry to disturb you
during your working hour.

644
00:42:03,960 --> 00:42:05,630
I'll go take care of my work too then.

645
00:42:10,970 --> 00:42:14,270
Sir, I prepared coffee... Have a good day.

646
00:42:23,310 --> 00:42:26,420
Why did your dad just leave?

647
00:42:26,620 --> 00:42:27,850
He didn't even drink coffee.

648
00:42:30,050 --> 00:42:32,540
Did you two have a fight?

649
00:42:33,520 --> 00:42:34,920
Is it because of me?

650
00:42:36,490 --> 00:42:38,980
It's not that. Don't mind it.

651
00:42:40,330 --> 00:42:42,370
It doesn't seem so to me.

652
00:42:44,900 --> 00:42:47,350
He got upset because of me, right?

653
00:42:48,170 --> 00:42:51,850
My dad and I aren't compatible,
so we clash every time we meet.

654
00:42:53,110 --> 00:42:54,310
It's nothing to be proud of.

655
00:42:55,180 --> 00:42:57,840
So there's no need for you
to be worried about it.

656
00:43:07,390 --> 00:43:09,840
We have all the documentary evidence,
so let's indict him.

657
00:43:10,260 --> 00:43:11,860
It's finally time to indict him.

658
00:43:12,030 --> 00:43:14,250
Shall we go out for lunch now?

659
00:43:14,330 --> 00:43:16,070
That sounds good.
Let's go eat something tasty.

660
00:43:16,260 --> 00:43:19,700
Since you all worked hard,
let's go and eat something nice.

661
00:43:20,140 --> 00:43:21,910
- How about beef?
- Beef?

662
00:43:22,670 --> 00:43:24,790
- Sure.
- This is Mr. Kim's office.

663
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:27,460
Yes, sir.

664
00:43:30,010 --> 00:43:31,030
What?

665
00:43:41,190 --> 00:43:42,650
What's making you hesitate so much?

666
00:43:43,460 --> 00:43:45,070
I wonder what kind of shocking story it is.

667
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:51,850
Alright, I'll be honest with you
and cut to the chase.

668
00:43:52,930 --> 00:43:55,930
The Jung Ji Ho case. Wrap it up quickly.

669
00:44:00,710 --> 00:44:02,860
I want to wrap it up more than anyone else.

670
00:44:02,980 --> 00:44:06,220
So I'm starting to make
progress bit by bit.

671
00:44:06,350 --> 00:44:08,360
I looked over the case too,

672
00:44:08,550 --> 00:44:10,590
and all Jung Ji Ho did was
gamble abroad illegally.

673
00:44:11,090 --> 00:44:13,310
There isn't enough evidence to prove...

674
00:44:13,420 --> 00:44:14,620
he embezzled the slush funds.

675
00:44:15,220 --> 00:44:18,600
The circumstances point out this was
the vice president's own doing.

676
00:44:21,500 --> 00:44:23,070
Is what you're saying the truth...

677
00:44:23,570 --> 00:44:25,470
or do we have to make it look that way?

678
00:44:27,570 --> 00:44:28,630
Is...

679
00:44:30,570 --> 00:44:32,040
the district attorney behind this?

680
00:44:32,440 --> 00:44:33,440
What?

681
00:44:33,440 --> 00:44:35,320
Attorney Choi Yoon Su who is
in charge of this case...

682
00:44:36,110 --> 00:44:37,410
is the district attorney's brother-in-law.

683
00:44:37,410 --> 00:44:39,190
What does that have to do with this?

684
00:44:39,480 --> 00:44:42,750
Just conclude that the embezzlement
was due to the vice president's...

685
00:44:42,750 --> 00:44:43,810
Sir!

686
00:44:46,050 --> 00:44:47,080
Sir.

687
00:44:47,120 --> 00:44:49,540
Don't you remember what you told me
when you brought me back?

688
00:44:50,030 --> 00:44:52,990
You said Jung Ji Ho's embezzlement
case would be difficult...

689
00:44:53,060 --> 00:44:55,040
to investigate if it weren't
for a nutcase like me.

690
00:44:55,060 --> 00:44:56,360
I know what you mean.

691
00:44:57,270 --> 00:44:59,580
I have no excuse whatsoever. But...

692
00:44:59,770 --> 00:45:01,480
this seems more complicated
than I expected.

693
00:45:03,610 --> 00:45:05,380
You went through a lot of
trouble to return to work.

694
00:45:05,540 --> 00:45:07,690
I'm just afraid this might
threaten your position too.

695
00:45:08,510 --> 00:45:09,600
Okay?

696
00:45:35,270 --> 00:45:36,740
Mr. Kwon.

697
00:45:37,340 --> 00:45:39,620
Did you call your dad?

698
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:41,210
Did he go home safely?

699
00:45:41,940 --> 00:45:45,250
I'm just worried he didn't get to
say what he came here to say...

700
00:45:45,250 --> 00:45:46,440
because of me.

701
00:45:47,420 --> 00:45:50,250
I don't think so. There was
no particular reason he came here.

702
00:45:50,720 --> 00:45:52,970
You're wrong. I remember...

703
00:45:53,120 --> 00:45:55,880
him saying that he came
to say something to you.

704
00:45:57,230 --> 00:45:58,290
What?

705
00:46:02,560 --> 00:46:05,050
- I have to take this call.
- Okay, then.

706
00:46:09,770 --> 00:46:12,160
Yes, Mom. I was about to...

707
00:46:15,910 --> 00:46:17,850
What? What happened to Dad?

708
00:46:18,580 --> 00:46:19,840
Your dad...

709
00:46:20,080 --> 00:46:23,900
revealed that the deputy mayor
embezzled 2.7 million dollars,

710
00:46:24,220 --> 00:46:25,750
and he was suspended for three months...

711
00:46:26,020 --> 00:46:27,900
for violating the Government Officials Act.

712
00:46:28,520 --> 00:46:30,740
He didn't tell you anything?

713
00:46:31,790 --> 00:46:33,830
He said he'd visit you
to discuss that matter.

714
00:46:33,830 --> 00:46:35,870
(Deputy Mayor Kim Jun Cheol should
withdraw his unfair suspension!)

715
00:46:53,580 --> 00:46:54,650
I'm here.

716
00:46:56,690 --> 00:46:59,170
What are you here for? How did you know?

717
00:46:59,650 --> 00:47:01,090
Mom told me.

718
00:47:01,120 --> 00:47:03,210
Your mom got nosy again.

719
00:47:04,360 --> 00:47:05,820
You must be busy, so get going.

720
00:47:05,860 --> 00:47:07,840
Let's go somewhere for a cup of coffee.

721
00:47:09,130 --> 00:47:11,010
Do you think I'm in a state to have coffee?

722
00:47:12,830 --> 00:47:15,900
You should at least protest
after warming up your body.

723
00:47:25,110 --> 00:47:26,510
That punk.

724
00:47:32,620 --> 00:47:34,200
There's no need to sigh.

725
00:47:35,060 --> 00:47:38,360
I'm actually glad that I was suspended.

726
00:47:38,990 --> 00:47:41,700
- What do you mean?
- Even though I exposed the truth,

727
00:47:41,700 --> 00:47:42,930
nothing changed.

728
00:47:43,260 --> 00:47:45,310
Everyone was trying to cover this issue up.

729
00:47:46,370 --> 00:47:49,430
But I was eventually
suspended for three months,

730
00:47:49,570 --> 00:47:52,370
and thanks to that, I have a
reason to justify my protest.

731
00:47:53,510 --> 00:47:54,530
Perhaps...

732
00:47:55,140 --> 00:47:57,970
this may be a chance to let the
world know about this matter.

733
00:48:02,050 --> 00:48:04,060
Did you request an appeal?

734
00:48:05,090 --> 00:48:06,380
When is the hearing?

735
00:48:06,620 --> 00:48:07,640
Tomorrow.

736
00:48:08,820 --> 00:48:10,390
What if your suspension is finalized?

737
00:48:12,030 --> 00:48:14,070
I'll file a lawsuit in order
to withdraw it.

738
00:48:14,730 --> 00:48:16,810
Is that why you came by to
the law firm earlier today?

739
00:48:19,070 --> 00:48:22,470
To ask me to defend you
in case you go to trial?

740
00:48:26,840 --> 00:48:28,680
Why didn't you tell me
that from the beginning?

741
00:48:30,650 --> 00:48:33,950
Did you even give me a chance to ask you?

742
00:48:35,020 --> 00:48:36,830
Still, you shouldn't have left like that.

743
00:48:37,120 --> 00:48:38,990
You always have a knack
for making me a bad son.

744
00:48:50,770 --> 00:48:52,570
So that's what happened.

745
00:48:55,070 --> 00:48:57,110
He must've been so upset,

746
00:48:57,310 --> 00:48:59,760
and I can't believe
I made a mistake like that.

747
00:49:03,140 --> 00:49:05,530
Don't worry about it.
It won't be a problem.

748
00:49:05,650 --> 00:49:09,020
Even if he gets suspended,
we can just file a lawsuit.

749
00:49:09,280 --> 00:49:11,570
I'll try my best to set things straight,

750
00:49:11,850 --> 00:49:13,560
so you don't have to be worried.

751
00:49:17,160 --> 00:49:18,320
I'm telling you, it's fine.

752
00:49:20,600 --> 00:49:22,270
It's not just that.

753
00:49:22,900 --> 00:49:25,430
I'm just worried that I might have...

754
00:49:25,430 --> 00:49:26,930
offended your father.

755
00:49:27,900 --> 00:49:31,010
If he finds out you're dating a
celebrity with a complicated past,

756
00:49:31,010 --> 00:49:32,270
he'll be worried sick.

757
00:49:34,310 --> 00:49:36,590
I totally ruined making a
good first impression.

758
00:49:42,250 --> 00:49:43,860
There's no reason to be upset.

759
00:49:45,620 --> 00:49:47,770
Once people know what
kind of person you are,

760
00:49:47,860 --> 00:49:49,760
there's no reason why
anyone wouldn't like you.

761
00:49:49,960 --> 00:49:52,410
There's a good reason you won
all those broadcasting awards.

762
00:50:01,670 --> 00:50:04,630
Then will your father go to
the hearing alone tomorrow?

763
00:50:04,940 --> 00:50:06,070
Yes.

764
00:50:06,610 --> 00:50:08,480
He'll make a personal statement...

765
00:50:08,480 --> 00:50:10,700
and listen to the details
regarding his suspension.

766
00:50:11,010 --> 00:50:13,100
There's no reason for me
to tag along tomorrow.

767
00:50:14,980 --> 00:50:16,150
I see.

768
00:50:18,550 --> 00:50:21,070
Your father might feel
nervous if he goes alone.

769
00:50:25,630 --> 00:50:28,100
What? You want me to go
to the hearing with him?

770
00:50:28,100 --> 00:50:29,390
No matter how much I think about it,

771
00:50:29,500 --> 00:50:31,680
your father will be too
nervous if he goes alone.

772
00:50:31,830 --> 00:50:34,870
So, as his son and
his attorney, you should...

773
00:50:34,870 --> 00:50:36,200
accompany him.

774
00:50:36,940 --> 00:50:39,420
I canceled all your morning appointments,

775
00:50:39,570 --> 00:50:40,630
so you should go.

776
00:50:41,610 --> 00:50:45,460
I appreciate the gesture,
but you don't seem to know him well.

777
00:50:45,850 --> 00:50:48,130
He's not someone to get nervous
over something like this.

778
00:50:48,650 --> 00:50:50,770
He's much stronger than me, mentally.

779
00:50:51,090 --> 00:50:53,130
That's what you think.

780
00:50:53,520 --> 00:50:56,930
No matter how strong he is,
everything must be new to him now.

781
00:50:57,460 --> 00:50:59,580
He might feel more nervous than usual,

